com.github.manosbatsis.vaultaire.plugin.rsql

Class RsqlConditionsVisitor<P extends StatePersistable,F extends Fields<P>>

  • com.github.manosbatsis.vaultaire.plugin.rsql.RsqlConditionsVisitor<P,F>

  • public class RsqlConditionsVisitor<P extends StatePersistable,F extends Fields<P>>

    Parses RSQL (a superset of FIQL) into interface Conditions that can be added to class VaultQueryCriteriaCondition. The latter can then generate complete Vault query criteria that takes the RSQL string into account.

    See also:

    • REST Query Language with RSQL

    • RSQL Parser

    • https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-nottingham-atompub-fiql-00

    See Also:
    interface Condition, class VaultQueryCriteriaCondition, REST Query Language with RSQL, RSQL Parser, https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-nottingham-atompub-fiql-00
